{"tid":232640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屢拖數　樂視系高層跳船","createTime":"2017-05-07T01:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T02:29:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9169d54fd51c4fb5311da165e860ff4ddbfc0c47","tid":232640,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20013547&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20013547%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170507&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=eef5795c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20013547%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170507&h=7f29764d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20013547&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170507</a><br />\n<br />\n屢拖數　樂視系高層跳船<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n樂視<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年樂視被爆資金鏈斷裂，董事長賈躍亭終承認資金面臨大挑戰，及後雖獲融創董事長孫宏斌等人泵水相助，惟仍陸續有拖數及高層跳船等事件。<br />\n上周有廣告公司入稟高等法院，指樂視體育香港拖欠去年8月至11月的廣告服務費用，至今仍未收到款項，涉款約385萬港元。<br />\n另外，集團旗下內地召車應用程式「易到用車」同樣出事，有使用該平台的司機反映，已經完成定單卻無法結算，收入亦未到賬，雖「易到」上月底表示融資進展順利，預料本月內解決提款問題，惟至今未有透露具體時間。<br />\n樂視系內地公司高層亦現離職潮。內地媒體昨報道，上任不足2個月，樂視超級汽車（LeSEE）CEO張海亮約於兩周前離職。早在今年3月，樂視汽車聯合創辦人丁磊以個人身體健康理由辭任。<br />\n■記者江靖然<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n3香港公開促樂視清還網絡服務費<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;3小時前"},{"pid":"6ff2583cf89566d9c23ee230dfaef867646da106","tid":232640,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:46:50.000Z","msg":"而家Android版youtube成日出佢既廣告"},{"pid":"192f2a9737387c9dc01f18008e05c911f3332c04","tid":232640,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03522d412650965da211db76a1b7ab70f32d43ac","tid":232640,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06bd795d8a51927d9a74a8145551f15f59e86f4","tid":232640,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:26:36.000Z","msg":"喜聞樂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搶左個仔英超轉播權，老豆幫你公開追佢數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e928dfc4360cddebd26ae9642de6d00d2bbe0a","tid":232640,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"期待更多以本傷人既大陸企業收皮"}]}